title: Baja Blast From The Past starring Trendan Frasier 6/25: Derek Chauvin, F9, J.D. Vance, Dragonman, Halloween Kills, Residential Schools
itunes:title: Baja Blast From The Past starring Trendan Frasier 6/25: Derek Chauvin, F9, J.D. Vance, Dragonman, Halloween Kills, Residential Schools
description:
In this edition of Baja Blast From The Past starring Trendan Frasier, Jack and Anna discuss Derek Chauvin's sentencing, the long-awaited release of 'F9', shitty author J.D. Vance's military advice for Gen. Mark Milley, the misleadingly named 'Dragonman' skull, the new 'Halloween' trailer, and a disturbing update on Canada's Residential Schools
